==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mattowacca
<hw>Mat`to*wac"ca</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Indian
name.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An American clupeoid fish
(<spn>Clupea mediocris</spn>), similar to the shad in habits and
appearance, but smaller and less esteemed for food; -- called also
<altname>hickory shad</altname>, <altname>tailor shad</altname>,
<altname>fall herring</altname>, and <altname>shad
herring</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mattress</ent>⟦br⟧
